CSEM_Api_Key_Description: Photo DNA Api Service Subscription Key (this app is only active with valid api key)
CSEM_Quarantine_Target_Channel_Descripti: Channel to move CSEM quarantined images to. Be sure to create this channel as documented.
CSEM_Limit_Analysis_To_Channels_Csv_Labe: Limit image analysis to specified channels
CSEM_Limit_Analysis_To_Channels_Csv_Desc: A comma separated values list of channels (e.g. "channelA,channelB") to limit image upload analysis to, all channels if empty
